{
  "url": "https://www.hymnal.net/cn/hymn/ch/497",
  "title": "神阿你名何等广大",
  "verses": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "神 阿，"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你 名 何"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "等 廣"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "大 泱"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "漭！"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我 今 投"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "身 其"
            },
            {
              "chord": "E",
              "text": "中， 心"
            },
            {
              "chord": "E7",
              "text": "頂 安"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "然；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "有 你"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "彀 了， 無 論 日 有 多"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "長；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "有 你"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "彀"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "了， 無"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "論 夜"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "有"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "多"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "暗。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "有你够了，无论事多纷烦；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "有你够了，无论境多寂寞；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "有你，我就已经能够尽欢，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "有你，我就已经能够唱歌。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你是我神！全有！全足！全丰！"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你能为我创造我所缺乏；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "有你自己，在我回家途中，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "无论有何需要，都必无差。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我的神阿，你在已过路上，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "曾用爱的神迹多方眷顾；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "故我敢再投入你的胸膛，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "因信心安，赞美你的道路。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "metadata": {
